      • finishRouting

        public void finishRouting()
        Inform that no more events will be routed in here, onRoutingFinished callback will be called as soon as there are no events in the router

      • onDelivery

        public void onDelivery(Packet packet)
        If packet was delivered successfully RoutingListener get notification with success.

        If packet was not delivered and has more options to try, it will be putted to the next step in route

        If packet delivery failed and packet does not have any other options, OnDelivery callback will be called with false.

        Sync threads at this point
